WEBVTT

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:31.856
(Laughter)

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:34.936
Ingolf told me
that when he waits for the bus

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:38.416
and the bus stops 10 meters away from him,

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:41.400
it was because the driver was a "raghead."

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:45.016
I recognized that feeling.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.320
When I was young

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.056
and I waited for the bus

00:05:49.080 --> 00:05:51.136
and it stopped 10 meters away from me,

00:05:51.160 --> 00:05:53.600
I was sure that the driver was a racist.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.696
When I got home,

00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:02.160
I was very ambivalent about my experience.